  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK300">
<l>yāmeyyāk kaṇṭavaṟṟu ḷillai yeṉaittoṉṟum</l>
<l>vāymaiyi ṉalla piṟa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Amidst all that we have seen (described) as real (excellence), there is nothing so good as truthfulness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
